Nagponchom' xraunnachea xudhd ponchmik monoitat. Xraunn mhoino suru zaun soglleant poilim yeupi ho utsou. Hea ponchmi disa ghoramni nagachi puza kortat, taka lagun tika ‘nagponchom'’ va ‘nagponchomi’ oxem namv poddlam. Ved kalla saun ho utsou monoit aileat. Hea sombondit sabar kanneo aikuvopak mellttat.

- xri krixnn jen'na kalika nagak porajit korun yomuna nhoinchea patallatlean sukhrup bhair ailo to dis xraunn xudhd ponchmicho axil'lo. Tea disa saun nagpuza korpak survat zali oxem mhonnttat.

- panch yugam poilim ‘sotyexvori’ namvachi ek devi axil'li. Ticho bhavo nagponchomichea adlea disa somvsarak ontorolo. Tea dukhan tinnem tea disa on'nacho konn pottant ghetlo na. Hea khatir, bhoinnin nagponchomichea adlea disa aplea bhavak dirgh ayuxy prapt zaunchem hea ud'dexan upvas korun devak magnneantolean vinoilo. Hea disa nagachi puza korpa fattlem karonn mhollear, sotyexvorik aplo bhavo tea disa nagrupat dislo. Ten'na tinnem tea nagrupak aplo bhavo manlo. Tea vellar nagdevan soput ghetlo ki, ji bhoinn taka bhavo manun tachi puza kortoli tichem to rokxonn kortolo. Haka lagun hea disa bailam nagrazachi puza kortat.
